text: John Payn (died 1402), of Wymondham, Norfolk, was an English politician. He married Sybil Hethersett of Hethersett, Norfolk. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Norfolk in 1401. ==References== Category:14th- century births Category:1402 deaths Category:English MPs 1401 Category:People from Wymondham Category:Members of the Parliament of England for Norfolk
